lead_paragraph: Nico Rosberg gave a hint of Mercedes' true speed on Tuesday, with the fastest time on the first day of Formula One's final pre-season test, and then said there was still room for improvement.

headline.print_headline: Rosberg Fastest but Says Mercedes Have More to Do
